Class LogoutRequestImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sun.identity.saml2.protocol.impl.RequestAbstractImpl
      • com.sun.identity.saml2.protocol.impl.LogoutRequestImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LogoutRequest, RequestAbstract

    public class LogoutRequestImpl
extends RequestAbstractImpl
implements LogoutRequest
    This class implements the LogoutRequest element in SAML protocol schema. It provides all the methods required by LogoutRequest
